fers to the cost of transferring money by your credit union, bank, or other business. If you wish to send $300 and the company charges a $15 transfer fee, the total cost will be $315. The firm will pocket the $15 as profit and send $300 to your celebration in another country.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The exchange rate is a technique of converting one country\u2019s money into another. For example, if the exchange rate between Australia and China is one dollar to 4.01 Chinese yuan, that will be the rate to change your money. If you wanted to send $200 to China at this exchange rate, your second party would receive 802 Chinese yuan.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The recipient pays for the cost of receiving the money. Some firms charge both the sender and receiver.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/six-send-money-options.jpg\" alt=\"six send money options\" class=\"wp-image-800\" srcset=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/six-send-money-options.jpg 800w, http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/six-send-money-options-300x150.jpg 300w, http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/six-send-money-options-768x384.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"6-best-international-money-transfer-service\"><\/span>6 Best International Money Transfer Service<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"1-paypal-best-for-local-and-large-amount-domestic-transfers\"><\/span>1. PayPal- Best for Local and Large-Amount Domestic Transfers<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Because of its accessibility and variety of payment methods, PayPal outperforms rival peer-to-peer (P2P) cash transfer platforms like Venmo and Zelle. Your money is quickly deposited into the <a href=\