t, or prepaid card.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"3-zelle-ideal-for-quick-domestic-bank-transfers\"><\/span>3. Zelle- Ideal for quick Domestic Bank Transfers<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Zelle is a fantastic peer-to-peer bank account transfer service. Wire transfers between banks can take days to complete; Zelle, on the other hand, can accomplish them in minutes. The Zelle Network currently has over <a href=\"https:\/\/www.forbes.com\/advisor\/banking\/best-ways-to-send-money\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">5,400 financial firms<\/a> on board, giving a large number of individuals access to rapid and fee-free bank transactions. During the second quarter of 2019, Zelle processed over 171 million transactions totaling $44 billion in transfers.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>For you to use Zelle, sign up for the service directly through your bank\u2019s app or website, and then register your profile. If your bank isn\u2019t already partnered with Zelle, you can still use its iOS and Android apps to access the service. However, the receiver must be a customer bank institution collaborating with Zelle.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"4-western-union-the-oldest-way-to-send-and-receive-money\"><\/span>4. Western Union- The oldest Way to Send and Receive Money<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The transfer fees can be as little as five dollars depending on the quantity of cash being sent, but the exchange rate inflation rate might be as high as 6%. However, if you need to transfer cash to a remote location, the benefits of using Western Union may outweigh the drawbacks. Furthermore, Western Union is the only realistic alternative for some people because of the large number of sites and the ability to pick up cash in person rather than by bank transfer, even if they complain about the high costs.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can utilize various services to conduct transactions after you register for a Western Union free account or log in to your profile. You can pay with a bank account, a debit card or credit2, or even <a href=\"https:\/\/www.paymentscardsandmobile.com\/western-union-provide-mobile-money-transfer-viber\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">a mobile phone<\/a> to transfer the money to another bank account, a mobile phone, or an agent location.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"5-remitly-ideal-for-sending-cash-to-the-developing-countries\"><\/span>5. Remitly- Ideal for Sending Cash to the Developing Countries<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Remitly is a cost-effective solution if you\u2019re sending money to a bank account in another country and wish to send it straight in the destination country\u2019s currency. The service for transferring cash to developing countries also guarantees a delivery time and a refund. Remitly\u2019s expedited option, which costs $3.99 and can transfer funds in minutes, is a huge advantage, and it additionally offers a home delivery option to your receiver.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"6-wise-multi-currency-and-borderless-account\"><\/span>6. Wise- Multi-Currency and Borderless Account<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Initially referred to as TransferWise. It is a cash transfer option that enables you to transfer and receive funds from millions of people worldwide. They offer a straightforward fee structure and a near-to-mid-market exchange rate. In most nations across the globe, you can receive or send money from a bank account. Whether you transfer it through its Borderless and multi-currency account, your money is safe.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Wise\u2019s borderless bank account is free to open and requires a $25 deposit to get started. The bank has marked its segments for a specific currency. For example, if you put a euro balance, the bank account will be assigned a <a href=\"https:\/\/thepaypers.com\/expert-opinion\/instant-global-payments-are-the-future-of-money--1254528\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">SWIFT number<\/a>, just as it would in Europe. Consequently, a sort code will be assigned to the cash if you put a GBP balance. Over 40 currencies can be held and controlled in the bank account.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"send-and-receive-money-through-international-money-transfer-options\"><\/span>Send and Receive Money Through International Money Transfer Options<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Transferring cash to some countries worldwide can be challenging; not all money transfer providers are available in every country. Some don\u2019t offer competitive exchange rates. Finding a cash pick-up site near your receiver might be tricky. The challenge gives you more reason to try those transfer service options mentioned above to send and receive money abroad fast and safely.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>For a complete list of payment options, visit Verv. It is a Novatti Group trademark that provides clients in Europe and beyond with a long-term solution. It provides a comprehensive set of services for businesses and individuals who would like to approach payments with expertise, vision, and purpose.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>The best money transfer service options to send and receive money abroad. Get a safe money transfer service for sending, receiving, money!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":799,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[24,16,14],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/735"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/